GA WDI NYC Jan 14, Project 1

Overview

IN DEVELOPMENT
http://tadaya.herokuapp.com/

ProjectOne is an app that allows users to checkin to places and tag them with descriptors. Users can see real-time what is trending in their area without have to read long or outdated reviews.


Technologies Used

Ruby 2.1.0
Ruby on Rails 4.0.2
PostgreSQL Database
Authentication & Authorization from scratch using bcrypt-ruby
Google Place API
Google Maps API
Word Cloud Maker API (Unirest Client Library)
HTTParty

User Stories:
- As a user, I can find a location so that I can review/tag it
- As a user, I can check into place 
- As a user, i can tag a place when I check in
- As a user, I can browse places and see tags associated to places
- As a user, I can add a new place
- As a user, I can log in and out

Backlog
- Improve Location Entry and Accuracy
- Lock tags to predefined set

A full list of user stories can be found by looking at this Pivotal Tracker Project (https://www.pivotaltracker.com/s/projects/1015702)